{\rm Y} = {\beta ^{\prime}_{\rm task \cdot\, regressor}}_{\rm task} + {\beta_{\rm GM\,regressor}}_{\rm GM} + {\rm \varepsilon^{\prime}}
\end{eqnarray*}
$$\end{document}

Thus, the “cleaned” data are represented as
